      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CLOCK IT (6) is an honest type in the frame at six of 14 starts including last time when third (17.82) over 324m at this track. Rates highly here and will go close. DESPICABLE KYRO (1) had been racing well without winning, recording three minors on end before finding traffic last time and finishing fifth in a NG at this track (17.67). Rates a leading chance on best. DESPICABLE MILO (3) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at Richmond behind Live And Free (18.80) in a Grade 5. Has the pace to be prominent. The form out of his last race has been franked. Expected to be in this for a long way. REEL 'EM HARADA (2) cannot be ruled out.",
